{
  "stem": "8786.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were supposed to send out to there-- to that place, except at the border, as we got to the border [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a Hungarian police officer, high-- high-ranking officer, said, what are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have-- you are actually kosher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What's wrong with you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, don't ask me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We don't--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, he sent us back over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is in 1941.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we tasted it already, this what it means.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And saying the truth, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] many, many Polish Jews were coming to Hungary escaping.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they told us stories, horrible stories.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I will not deny the fact that I am ashamed of it today.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were so naive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm not talking me as a young boy, but in general the Jewish community and the leadership was naive enough [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they didn't take it seriously.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All these warnings, they came down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They tell us stories, terrible stories, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and they didn't want believe it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If Budapest or the Jewish leadership would believe those things, then we didn't have to wait 'til 1944 when they came and took us away.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is-- this is how I feel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it's a painful topic to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it was the-- it was-- it was very naive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The people were very naive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The Jewish people were always optimistic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But in this case I think it was more than optimism.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The Hungarian Jews, they thought of themselves that they are-- after all, we are great patriots.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We are important for the government.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They're not going to do to us what they did to the Polish Jews or to the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In other words, they were cocksure of themselves that it couldn't happen here.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
